Very interesting, Mike. I&#39;m not sure if you know about Psychometry or not, but it would be worth a few minutes of your time to research. Just google it. 

I think spirits tend to be around, maybe not everywhere at any given time, but when trying to contact a particular spirit, it could be important to have an object that had any sort of physical involvement with that spirit. I can&#39;t think of the right word at the moment, but it&#39;s sort of like a beacon. Their energy is attached to it and when you try to communicate, they can go to where their energy is. It possibly provides a better medium for them to communicate?

That&#39;s just kind of my thought process on it. No hard facts, just my understanding. Any input on these thoughts would be great. Must...break...now...brain...hurts...

Jeremy




